# This file keeps the models/ directory tracked by git.
# Place the following trained model files here to enable real predictions:
#
#   drugmirror_models.pkl   – dict mapping label names to sklearn estimators
#   label_cols.pkl          – list of 12 side-effect category names
#   feature_cols.pkl        – ordered list of training feature column names
#
# The backend will automatically detect these files on startup and switch
# from MOCK mode to REAL prediction mode — no code changes required.
